title: THE Steve Wilkos Show 06.27.08
description:
ENCORE OF JAILED FOR LIFE:
--------------------------
    In 1987 a 4 year-old boy named Lattie McGee was tortured and beaten by his mother&#039;s boyfriend whom she met at a homeless shelter. The courts found that Lattie&#039;s mother didn&#039;t do anything to stop it, and that Lattie was the victim of this abuse for 2 1/2 months before he eventually died. Now 20 years later Lattie&#039;s mother finally speaks.
